Manchester United take on Manchester City in the derby on Sunday . 
  United manager Louis van Gaal says Robin van Persie is not yet fit enough to play . 
  Van Persie said he was fit to play after ankle trouble but Van Gaal has ruled him out . 
  Luke Shaw is also yet to be fully fit for the game . 
  Van Gaal says he has been dreaming of beating City at Old Trafford . 
  Manchester City beat United 1-0 in the Premier League on Saturday . 
 